snippet.title: Rs 500 and Rs 1000 Notes Worth Rs 91 Lakhs Seized from Maharashtra Minister's Car

localized.description:
Rs 500 and Rs 1000 notes worth Rs 91 lakhs seized from Maharashtra cabinet minister's vehicle. Police suspect this money would be used in elections.
